msgstr "<code>record</code>: Registro actual (el registro del formulario)."

#. module: web_form_banner
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:web_form_banner.view_web_form_banner_rule_form
msgid ""
"<code>record_id</code>: Integer id of the record being edited, or <code>False</code> if the form\n"
